<!--
https://forum.shotcut.org/t/some-titling-filter-sets/39110

add a color, picture or video in a empty track then apply the filter set for a lower third with 
gradient texture, the color in the second filter gradient determinate the color of the lower third, 
you can it animate with the “mask : from file” and you can use 
texture of video or picture if you change the parameter “fusion mode” in the gradient filter
-->
